But shinsuke...

44
00:02:45,652 --> 00:02:51,002
you know you're not in a position turn away people with previous marriage experience

45
00:02:51,002 --> 00:02:52,424
Yes I know

46
00:02:52,424 --> 00:02:53,739
Don't worry it's ok!

47
00:02:53,739 --> 00:02:55,660
Marriage happens by fate

48
00:02:55,660 --> 00:02:56,604
All of a sudden,

49
00:02:56,604 --> 00:02:59,696
