50
00:02:59,696 --> 00:03:02,122
It would be nice if that was the case...

51
00:03:02,122 --> 00:03:03,876
It's ok don't worry!

52
00:03:03,876 --> 00:03:08,014
Ikuyo-san, how about living with Shinsuke until then?

53
00:03:08,014 --> 00:03:09,609
No thank you!

54
00:03:09,609 --> 00:03:11,885
Not with this cold selfish guy

55
