How about living with Keiko?

56
00:03:13,324 --> 00:03:14,308


57
00:03:14,308 --> 00:03:17,108
Well that would be 100 times better

58
00:03:17,108 --> 00:03:17,584


59
00:03:17,584 --> 00:03:19,293
Since Yumi is there too

60
00:03:19,293 --> 00:03:22,084
That's right
I wish you'd live with us too

61
00:03:22,084 --> 00:03:24,803
- Right, honey?
- Uh.. umm yeah.

62
00:03:24,803 --> 00:03:29,751


63
00:03:29,751 --> 00:03:32,666
