64
00:03:32,666 --> 00:03:36,960
It's because you're making them.

65
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,348
Hey honey

66
00:03:38,348 --> 00:03:41,332
- What kind of reaction was that?
- Hrmm what?

67
00:03:41,332 --> 00:03:44,243
Your face changed
You don't want to live with her, right?

68
00:03:44,243 --> 00:03:46,282
No that's not it

69
00:03:46,282 --> 00:03:49,031


70
00:03:49,031 --> 00:03:53,591
Don't worry
I have no plan to leave my current home

71
00:03:53,591 --> 00:03:58,360
