75
00:04:04,998 --> 00:04:05,985
What?

76
00:04:05,985 --> 00:04:07,688
You don't need a ride?

77
00:04:07,688 --> 00:04:10,264
I want to get away from these people as soon as possible

78
00:04:10,264 --> 00:04:10,979
Later

79
00:04:10,979 --> 00:04:14,546


80
00:04:14,546 --> 00:04:16,261
Even in an ash vase,

81
00:04:16,261 --> 00:04:18,567
I don't want to live with him

82
00:04:18,567 --> 00:04:20,105


83
00:04:20,105 --> 00:04:22,001
You're going to have separate entrances?

84
00:04:22,001 --> 00:04:23,448
Of course

85
00:04:23,448 --> 00:04:25,241
Even though it's a multi-family home,

86
00:04:25,241 --> 00:04:27,297
we still need our prviacy

87
00:04:27,297 --> 00:04:32,166
Why do you need two entrances for one house?

88
00:04:32,166 --> 00:04:35,705
Inside, we can build a door that connects two units

89
00:04:35,705 --> 00:04:40,062
Isn't it nice just that fact that we'll be living together

90
00:04:40,062 --> 00:04:42,770


91
00:04:42,770 --> 00:04:44,874
We run into this issue even at work

92
00:04:44,874 --> 00:04:46,722
Today is an aging society,

93
00:04:46,722 --> 00:04:49,646
so we'll be seeing more houses with 2 generations living together

94
00:04:49,646 --> 00:04:52,712
Maybe we should build a ring inside so they can duke it out

95
00:04:52,712 --> 00:04:55,347
Ring instead of a living (room) huh...

96
00:04:55,347 --> 00:04:56,779
After seeing these,

97
00:04:56,779 --> 00:05:00,267
it makes me want to avoid living with them after marrying

98
00:05:00,267 --> 00:05:03,230
Well my parents don't want to live with me anyway

99
00:05:03,230 --> 00:05:05,054
Aren't you forgetting something?

100
00:05:05,054 --> 00:05:07,381
After marrying, it's not just your own parents

101
00:05:07,381 --> 00:05:09,159
You now have the in-laws too

102
00:05:09,159 --> 00:05:10,541
Ah that's true

103
00:05:10,541 --> 00:05:14,002
When you get married, the number of parents and relatives,

104
00:05:14,002 --> 00:05:16,194
even by simple math doubles

105
00:05:16,194 --> 00:05:18,445
It's bad enough putting up with your own parents

106
00:05:18,445 --> 00:05:23,121
I think it would be nice to play a good daughter in-law

107
00:05:23,121 --> 00:05:25,672
saying, "mother~"

108
00:05:25,672 --> 00:05:28,222
You look like the type who will poison her in-law

109
00:05:28,222 --> 00:05:29,382


110
