114
00:05:35,759 --> 00:05:37,751
What?

115
00:05:37,751 --> 00:05:39,184
I think it's summer fatigue

116
00:05:39,184 --> 00:05:41,937


117
00:05:41,937 --> 00:05:43,862
Suffering from summer fatigue?

118
00:05:43,862 --> 00:05:44,874


119
00:05:44,874 --> 00:05:46,408
Yes

120
00:05:46,408 --> 00:05:47,513
Me too

121
00:05:47,513 --> 00:05:48,547
Huh?

122
00:05:48,547 --> 00:05:53,241
I feel tired and have no energy

123
00:05:53,241 --> 00:05:55,837
This is the first time I've seen a doctor describe her own symptom to a patient

124
00:05:55,837 --> 00:05:59,641
Anybody can suffer from summer fatigue

125
00:05:59,641 --> 00:06:03,266
Having a good routine,sleeping, eating properly...

126
00:06:03,266 --> 00:06:04,801
and drinking regularly...

127
00:06:04,801 --> 00:06:07,620
is the only way to beat it

128
00:06:07,620 --> 00:06:10,213
- I'm already doing that
- Please continue to do it

129
00:06:10,213 --> 00:06:10,945


130
00:06:10,945 --> 00:06:13,232
Doctor is powerless, huh

131
00:06:13,232 --> 00:06:17,265
Are you incapable of not saying asinine things when you're being examined?

132
00:06:17,265 --> 00:06:19,877
I see you still have energy left to get angry

133
00:06:19,877 --> 00:06:21,049


134
00:06:21,049 --> 00:06:25,821
I need to recharge before the next patient so please...

135
00:06:25,821 --> 00:06:26,341


136
00:06:26,341 --> 00:06:29,904
Looks like I got worse after coming here

137
00:06:29,904 --> 00:06:37,002


138
