Excuse me
Isn't it a bit hot in here?

139
00:06:39,813 --> 00:06:41,101
I'm sorry

140
00:06:41,101 --> 00:06:43,767
Somebody said it's too cold...

141
00:06:43,767 --> 00:06:44,393


142
