Please

154
00:07:31,326 --> 00:07:43,718


155
00:07:43,718 --> 00:07:45,635
What are you doing here?

156
00:07:45,635 --> 00:07:46,128


157
00:07:46,128 --> 00:07:48,374
I have something to tell you

158
00:07:48,374 --> 00:07:49,015


159
